{
  "stem": "10818.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there are-- there are parts of Nazism which appeal to the people who had been through a depression, through a lost war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He promised revenge for the lost war, and he promised jobs for everyone, which he managed to do by building armaments and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, there weren't any unemployed anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was-- there was a lot of positive perception on the part of the general populace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as the Jewish community was concerned, they were immediately aware that this was a dangerous thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I said, they thought it would blow over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never in their wildest dream-- I mean, who would've thought it could have come to extermination, and to all the things that it came to?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you just-- in-- in the 19th-- in the 20th century, these things didn't happen anymore, and certainly not in a civilized country like Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, this was the country of Goethe and of Beethoven.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, you can't believe that this is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in a sense, what you're saying is that they functioned in denial?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't-- it was denial in the sense, if they could have foreseen the future, it would have been denial.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't foresee just how bad it was going to get.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, yes, they said, this can't last forever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something's going to happen that maybe the outside nations-- England, France, will interfere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the night of Kristallnacht, I remember we listened to the radio.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got shortwave radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After all, that's not-- France was not very far away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Luxembourg broadcast in German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they mentioned that this had happened, and it had happened on the anniversary of the Peace of 1918.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
